function renderDossierPaths(items){return'<div class="list">'+((items||[]).map(function(x){return'<div class="card">'+chainPathVisual(x)+'<div class="toolbar">'+(x.dossier_ids||[]).map(function(id){return'<a class="button-sm" href="/dossier/'+encodeURIComponent(id)+'">打开边档案</a>'}).join('')+'</div></div>'}).join('')||'<div class="empty">没有已有机制路径。</div>')+'</div>'}
